<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.11">
<l>ūṭal kūṭa luṇartal puṇartalai</l>
<l>nīṭu niṉṟa niṟaipuka ḻāycciyar</l>
<l>kūṭa laikkuḻaṟ kōtaimuṉ kūṟiya</l>
<l>pāṭal pattumval lārkkillai pāvamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There [shall] be no sins</l>
<l>for those capable [of mastering] the ten songs</l>
<l rend="indent">spoken by Kōtai with curling hair in the past</l>
<l rend="indent">about the union of the cowherdesses with long-lasting, abundant fame,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and their] being with love quarrel, realisation, [and] union.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
